{
  "stem": "9601.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I forgave him a while ago, because just died recently.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So you got-- the-- the dead ones you got to forgive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he went away over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But they had a sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My father and Uncle Chaim had a sister hidden not far from where Uncle Chaim was-- was hidden.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, the hero of the expedition was my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She went to find out, you know, how Aunt-- Aunt Chaika is surviving.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She came there, and she came back with Aunt Chaika.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Aunt Chaika must have weighed 150, maybe 170, a big woman, bigger than my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And my father was no slouch, and [? here ?] a bigger woman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I don't know how old she was, but she was a big lady.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can you get-- imagine to get the woman up to the-- through that little hole up into the attic?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She came, and she stayed with us for a while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She stayed with us for the rest of the expedition, till we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One day sometimes in-- I don't know, July, August, sometimes in the summer, Stakh came and told us that we have to leave, because there are rumors that the freedom fighters are going burn down the estate.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's up to you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You want to stay, you can stay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You-- you want to get fried?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A little side-- a side story to that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Germans used to come and inspect, you know, the estate to see whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Naturally most of them were officers, right?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You don't send a-- a plain soldier.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He's needed on the front.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were ladies in the thing and in the village.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of the ladies was the daughter of the deacon of the church.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
